WEBVTT

00:04:30.458 --> 00:04:35.768
Now anyone that walks by Trump Tower
can see Colin Kaepernick take a knee

00:04:35.792 --> 00:04:37.351
in augmented reality,

00:04:37.375 --> 00:04:39.351
and there's nothing they can do about it.

00:04:39.375 --> 00:04:41.268
(Laughter)

00:04:41.292 --> 00:04:43.934
Representation matters.

00:04:43.958 --> 00:04:46.559
Serena Williams proved to the world

00:04:46.583 --> 00:04:49.559
that a black girl from Compton
can dominate a sport

00:04:49.583 --> 00:04:52.809
that's traditionally played
at exclusive country clubs.

00:04:52.833 --> 00:04:54.208
Let's celebrate her now.

00:04:55.208 --> 00:04:56.684
Jackie Robinson.

00:04:56.708 --> 00:04:58.976
He broke the color barrier

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:03.476
and empowered many black athletes
to play in Major League Baseball.